 future people no weight" style="edgeStyle=none;curved=1;html=1;endArrow=block;endFill=1;strokeColor=#9aa6b3;fontSize=9;fontColor=#5b6675;strokeColor=#8a5fb0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="w1_5_6_11_16" target="w1_5_6_11_16_17"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="1624" y="991"/><mxPoint x="1654" y="1037"/></Array></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="e9" value="give merely-possible future people no weight" style="edgeStyle=none;curved=1;html=1;endArrow=block;endFill=1;strokeColor=#9aa6b3;fontSize=9;fontColor=#5b6675;strokeColor=#8a5fb0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="w1_5_6_11_14_16" target="w1_5_6_11_14_16_17"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="1299" y="990"/><mxPoint x="1310" y="1036"/></Array></mxGeometry></mxCell><mxCell id="e10" value="give merely-possible future people no weight" style="edgeStyle=none;curved=1;html=1;endArrow=block;endFill=1;strokeColor=#9aa6b3;fontSize=9;fontColor=#5b6675;strokeColor=#8a5fb0;" edge="1" parent="1" source="w1_5_6_11_15_16" target="w1_5_6_11_15_16_17"><mxGeometry relative="1" as="geometry"><Array as="points"><mxPoint x="974" y="990"/><mxPoint x="968" y="1036"/></Array></mxGeometry></mxCell><object label="Resilience erodes&lt;br&gt;nuclear deterrence&lt;br&gt;[1+5+6+11]&lt;br&gt;→ AI safety (Redwood Research)&lt;br&gt;   265k lives-eq/$1k · 72% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up ALLFED · 28%&lt;br&gt;(Sam Peltzman, Luisa Rodriguez)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + resilience_undermines_deterrence&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Peltzman effect for civil defence: making nuclear war survivable weakens deterrence and raises the chance of war, so a resilient-food dollar partly insures against a catastrophe it also makes marginally likelier. An alternative, lower estimate for ALLFED, anchored to Rodriguez&#x27;s ~0.4%/yr US-Russia war probability. Requires future people to be in the circle. || Chain