ecipice; the multiplanetary-backup argument). Mutually exclusive with the view that early expansion re-arms the hazard. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 11 resilience_undermines_deterrence → 14 time_of_perils_exit" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1z2kgS%2Fitdrts78IEs8Q4%2Bb5UT493U2k4KO7W1FVJkkAaYs6TRzYyQSdb727dnRgJhw5kqviRYanU%2F3f109%2FT8OAnojKShes8DejI4OTuDi4sLeBCExaA4%2BIJ8X%2BGPLIZx2nC9FmRchMGS0Qwyb9KedCaeN8HHFal4Al6rqr8fx6jnUso0ShTjMfgLVDcAFxIiuL9gJNTavH4DPJgRMSEZWU0WaURiWbxowyxVqaD540lElKJikjG1mARM%2BjyNFYvnhXgHYl5%2BPtn6em3NA0ElCxmNfTpJ44CKiMVUTgKKyoV%2BuhZtgWIRnfDZJKGChXJCn5gyjg2JvwCy8Y5JIPBppRb4e8ZCChi6zWt5BmpBFJAgkDU0j%2FHWJoELo0zQOgaFRBoAk%2FhcLaiN178khiD2jY5z8HmUcKk9Xgvgt9oDGuAjJo02qUgckJDHFCJMaOjAt3W%2BhstvGqr%2BnD4l1Ff44ZKEKQU%2BMxo2qXWMsndUKpimKzCB0h9KWnZsAJcfQJIZVSuojGiQcR7ACIWI8BdVq%2BOX4d1wdPkwvILpCuY0poIo6iSrgk00YGorWKf4sobJVBaSjidqMro%2BY3qE0o5HXCCF1nGTVtYGhSQJ5lc6cL%2BKnJDPYy4iElZ%2BJO0aJP32c9XoMjnruz%2FB%2Bw%2FnRnJKFbFPE8GnZIokUQhkyrXzgS6FL24NvK8OXBNfcbRJBLWqUCDRmYhVDSQHqunBxRzzN%2FySXV3e%2FHH2j68wpSHPkOz6W5Nn%2BoS%2FwxV%2BjroxtkYX2g5SX9mMYA4pkhfdt2S%2ByukNF1g2oKXxYV2zFP4NPlFEKsET%2FEyXSpwSQ07NSSLqVkOe78qIRJKuzu4xdjH85f50thKwlHDHRbAgqYS%2FPKetH56joQtMBhSVhcHblModVbfYOZiOt0C5VwHHinc8E%2FUBeI73XDWo5QIjpz28vLm5Hl5hmKbIixnyQKZiyZaa46V6pAJpj15UPtFQfcdqPocRDwSbp%2FQ7YndaBv3n%2B%2FoolZIRyIiongPSJISfvYLwWMJL5ImuCgxZKVayrng9YorNkZcYRIl5sPU%2BxHJ%2Fy71G7lzTLXzzSUjraVIkcF1oefyZfbwg34kIIEPqICn8kGtCkBn6DJE1SWLko1iBpEqFNEJuQeWjCDBYJt%2Bo3qI8x1D5HEMVEm1mI44Ei%2FFvDGa45TAg%2Bx6reUVdMYHwgM5m%2Bj8Mcom7iWCRRmCT4zP8XYN3w%2BuPo6GtP6Mho2y%2B0A23hlWMxRNxbbyO3dpfIJ51vOD%2B8%2B3t5egPGxhsh9YIdpxHGhhNU66oDxVNebi8u0KqCkYMAXShVB14QPCzNAzzIqpPV3X7C0Mg2NLS3bYVCw1HhXXIihmf%2BJLGRivR0eGpsB1ft6KQLTELeuyhoZDFBTD5v5TNMYpnBqE8%2Bw8LfnaKh7bNmrpHAiPbdENDx1HNx7shYCKtrbzXk0D3QYpcXG26LU4FgjZ1h0XfWYy2jQbsC1bStvJxjHiT35iObHxFwtUnKj7LYDczO06n0e83e%2B1%2Bz2s0u65H6247Z6vruK7X7