are simulated, the astronomical future that justified x-risk work probably gets switched off long before it happens. The same expected-value reasoning that bought astronomical stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 11 resilience_undermines_deterrence → 14 time_of_perils_exit → 16 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1T4zgS%2Fitd1O1dwiXGznvCsVUMhN2pA4YCpra2hqmMYiuJFtvySTImM8v%2B9mtJduKAc6QuX2aC3X766Xe1fhwEdEbSUJ3xgB6MDo6O4OTkBO4FYTEoDr4g35f4I4vhIW25XgcyLsLgidEMMm%2FSnfQmnjfxOhOvBzWpeAJer64hHmKEOpUyjRLFeAz%2BAhFH4EJCBPcXjIQa0Bu2wIMZEROSkeVkkUYklsWLLsxSlQqaP55ERCkqJhlTi0nApM%2FTWLF4Xoj3IObl55ONr1faPBBUspDR2KeTNA6oiFhM5SSgCC7005VoBxSL6ITPJgkVLJQT%2BszU6m0PQvak9bB4IlmUhkQbauweE38BZG08k0DgZqkW%2BHvGQgro3PVreQRqQRSQIJANZIcR0YyACwMmaBN9RiLNj0l8rhbUuvMfEj0U%2BwbjGHweJVxqh6wE8FttIA3wEZMGTSoSByTkMYUIQx468G0V0fHTN01Vf06fE%2Bor%2FPCJhCkFPjMI6%2BA7BuwDlQqm6RKMH%2FWHkpYNG8HpR5BkRtUSarc0yDgP4BaFiPAXdYvxy%2Fh6fHt6Pz6H6RLmNKaCKOokyyLfaIA%2BLzvrEF82MNbKUtL%2BRCSD9RmjJ5Q2POICM2zlN2llrVNIkmD4pQN3y8gJ%2BTzmIiJh7UfSbUAy7L7UDZaJ2dD9Cc4%2BHhvJKVXEPk0En5Ip5pBCIlOujQ90sXxxG%2BB9deCC%2BIqjTiKohUKBREciVg2QHKhODy7mGL%2Fxl%2Bz89PL3o799hSkNeYa1oL81cabP%2BDtc4ueIjb41WKg7SH1lI4IxpJjbaL7N9fM8%2B%2BEEqwq0ND5s6iSGf4JPFJFK8AQ%2F05UUpyZhQeckEU2LkMe7dksiSZdHd%2Bi7GP5yfzpaCniScM1FsCCphL88p6sfHqOiEwwGFIWHzltX0jVVV9hbmPa3QLk3DseG4HjG6yPwHO%2BlbljLBXpOW3h6eXkxPkc3TTEvZpgHMhVPpuigVK5UYNqjFbUbGqrvWOzHcMsDweYp%2FY7cnY5h%2F%2FmueZtKyQhkRNSPAdMkhJ%2B9IuGxwp8wT3RVoMtKvpJNxZsRU2yOeYlOlBgH2w7G2A3eM6%2BVG9d2C9t8EtJmmhQBXBVa7n9mHy%2FIdyICyDB1MCn8kOuEIDO0GSKrksSYj2IJkioV0ghzC2qfRIDOMvFGeMvyGF3lc3QV9idUsxbHBIvxb3RmuGEwYPY9YhjXPe2M64aaIoOTVSXUMGxDa9JNbS0KIsVei%2B1ljug8nS9gxk1j0DmW21gvSvsD1yojaLluO6%2FgcybQHUBnM%2F0f4pVqJREs0hbbZPAZ%2Fm7Ah%2F