er away than boosterism assumes (Weinersmiths, A City on Mars) — so below a large number of independent settlements, expansion ADDS anthropogenic risk, and accelerating it before geopolitics matures is net-negative. The perils window stays open far longer, the expected future shrinks, and x-risk work keeps its urgency but loses most of its astronomical multiplier. Mutually exclusive with the time-of-perils-exit reading. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 11 resilience_undermines_deterrence → 15 space_expansion_backfires" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWG1v2zgS%2FiuD4PbOztmK5Hc7lwXSxtktLskWSYpi0RQuLVEWL5KoIyk7bjf7229ISrac2Bsf%2FKV1JOqZZ95n%2BOMooCHJY%2FWeB%2FRodHRyAmdnZ3AvCEtBcfAF%2Bb7EH4sUHvKW63VgwUUczBldwMKbdCe9iedNvC7UpOIZeN26%2Fv4hRZxzKfMkU4yn4EcINwIXMiK4HzESazRv2AIPQiImZEGWkyhPSCrLF10Ic5ULWjyeJEQpKiYLpqJJwKTP81SxdFYe70HKq88nG1%2BvpHkgqGQxo6lPJ3kaUJGwlMpJQBFc6Kero12QGcFT9ClDBNRiMiX%2BY8gQwKg3Jn4EZK0jk0Dg41JF%2BDtkMQU04Pq1PAEVEQUkCGQDSaDVtWDgwoAJ2kTTkETTYBKfq4haq%2F1DoiFS32Ccgs%2BTjEut9%2BoAfqv1oAE%2BYpaaVCQNSMxTCgm6NXbg28pr4%2Fk3TVV%2FjppRX%2BGHcxLnFHhoENYOdgzYOyoVTPMlGHPpDyWtKjaC8w8gSUjVEmq3NFhwHsAtHiLCj%2BoW45fxzfj2%2FH58AdMlzGhKBVHUyZZlTNGAqQ1jHePLBrpUWUranohksD6hk4TSiidcYCCt7CbtWWsUkmXoZenA3TJxYj5LuUhIXPuRdRuQDbvPdYNlfDZ0f4L3H07NySlVxD7NBJ%2BSKYaKQiJTrpUPdEJ8cRvgfXXgkviKo0wiqIXCA5n2RKoaIDlQHR5czNB%2F4y%2BLi%2FOr30%2F%2B9hWmNOYLDHn9rfEzfcLf8RI%2FR2y0rcFC2UHuK%2BsR9CHFAET1bUhfFEEOZ5g8oE%2Fjw6ZiCYV%2Fgk8UkUrwDD%2FTCZPmxASnjkkimhah8HftliSSLk%2Fu0HYp%2FOn%2BdLIUMJdww0UQkVzCn57T1Q9PUdAZOgPK%2FELjrRPmhqprrB9M21vguVcGx7x3PGP1EXiO91w3rGWEltManl9dXY4v0ExTjIsQ40DmYs7mOsYrWUkF1zkItY80Vt8xp0%2FhlgeCzXL6Hbk7HcP%2B013zNpeSEVgQUT8FDJMYfvbKgM%2BomGOc6KxAk1VsJZuKNxOm2AzjEo0o0Q8m%2B98VKf%2B2hm6rUNF1eoWKSrBEW34j1woXLCJdIjBH0PerCqPLABGJJRuR70QEULugeZDSJRooyEnczE32oV04C064mDKFOcDSUGhdMGgQ%2FBQ%2BUywuQqJGkdQMIhN0As0dogz8QNI4bMo8DJmvayHGn6wX%2BXWB6mLs0TDU%2F%2BHHlUjOUCMil