5k lives-eq/$1k · 64% best&lt;br&gt;   runner-up ALLFED · 18%&lt;br&gt;(Nick Bostrom)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + resilience_undermines_deterrence + space_expansion_backfires + living_in_simulation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If most observers like us are simulated, the astronomical future that justified x-risk work probably gets switched off long before it happens. The same expected-value reasoning that bought astronomical stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 5 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 6 no_discounting_future_humans → 11 resilience_undermines_deterrence → 15 space_expansion_backfires → 16 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylWGtT20gW%2FSu3qJ1dm7WN5CeGZaoImJnUQiYFpFJTIeW0pbbVE0mt7ZZwnAzz2%2Fd0S7JlsBfX%2BktipKtzz3337R8HPp%2ByLEwvpM8PTg6Ojujs7IzuFRMxpZI8xb4v8GMe00PWdtwuzaUK%2FUfB5zR3x71xf%2By6Y7c3dvtU06lMyO3XDcRDDKhzrbMoSYWMyQuAeEIOJUxJLxAsNIDusE0uTZkaszlbjIMsYrEuX%2FRomqWZ4sXjccTSlKvxXKTB2Bfak1mcinhWivcpltXn47Wvl9pcUlyLUPDY4%2BMs9rmKRMz12OcAV%2BbpUrRHOmGQ4t8SIMCK8YR5X6cCAEuZPoXi0WgT8ViLKAuZMddaP2JeQGzlAqGJ0ftFGuD3VISc4OLVa31EacBSYr6vG%2BCIuBheJJUFU7wJz7HIsBQaz9OA5079h4afYs9inJIno0Rq45alAL41ZnIfj4S2aDplsc9CGXOKEPiwRV%2BWcR09fjFUzecwnHspPnxkYcZJTi3CKgVaFuwN1ylNsgVZb5oPNa8adkLnb0mzKU8XVLvl%2FlxKn24hxJQX1HOMX0bvRrfn96NLmixoxmOuWMpbyaLMOu6LdM1Zh3jZQMTTnJLxJ5As1gfEUKXG8Egq5NnSbzqXzZ3CkgRJoFt0t4haoZzFUkUsrP1Ieg1Khr2nusWyMRs6P9HF21MrOeEpy58mSk7YBJmUgshEGuN9UzKfnAa5n1t0xbxUQidTPIeCQGIiEacN0pK4SQ%2BpZojf6NP88vz696O%2FfaYJD%2BUcFWG%2BtXHm3%2FA7XOBzYMO3Fgu6%2FcxL84gghhz5CfPzjL8saoDOUFtkpPGwmYqI0z%2FJYynTqZIJPjP1FGc2YcnkJFPNHKGId%2B2WRZovju7gu5j%2Bcn46Wih61PROKj9gmaa%2F3FbPPDyFojMEg8ryg%2FNW9fSOpzfoMML4W0HuhcPRFlqu9foJuS33qW5Z6wCeMxaeX19fjS7hpgnyYoo80Jl6tEVHlaLlSpoSp